NAME

  Latin6 - Source code filter to escape Latin-6 script

SYNOPSIS

  use Latin6;

DESCRIPTION

  The Latin6 software provides character oriented Perl scripting
  environment in Latin-6 by easy installation and easy usage.

  - Character oriented regular expression
  - Byte oriented built-in functions
      and
  - Character oriented subroutines
  - Byte oriented regular expression on /b modifier

INSTALLATION

  Just copy Latin6.pm and Elatin6.pm to your @INC directory.
  for example, to C:\Perl\site\lib

SUBROUTINES

  Latin6::length(charstring)
  Latin6::substr(charstring, charpos, charlen)
  etc

SEE ALSO

  http://search.cpan.org/~ina/

